                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17320525-68-off344 t17320525-68-crimeloc342"></join>, two Books, called, The Antiquities of Westminster, Value 15 s. 1 Book called, The Antiquities of Rochester, Value 5 s. 3 Books called, The Antiquities of Surry, Value 25 s. and 12 other Books, Value 5 l. the Goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17320525-68-victim457" type="victimName">
                           Edmund 
                           Curll 
                        <interp inst="t17320525-68-victim457" type="surname" value="Curll"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17320525-68-victim457" type="given" value="Edmund"></interp>
